-US}}</ref> It is one of only three BTS stations to have island platforms, with the other being [[Siam BTS Station|Siam]] and [[Ha Yaek Lat Phrao BTS station|Ha Yaek Lat Phrao]].\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Bangkok Skytrain]]\n{{Sukhumvit Line navbox}}\n\n[[Category:BTS Skytrain stations]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 2017]]\n\n\n{{Bangkok-geo-stub}}\n{{Thailand-rail-transport-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Oum13928", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samrong_BTS_station"}
